---
// About section
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="about-layout">
      <div class="about-text reveal">
        <p class="section-label">About</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Building products<br />&amp; growing teams</h2>
        <p>
          I'm <strong>Raffaele</strong>, a Senior Engineering Manager at <strong>Quantilope</strong>
          in Munich, Germany. With over two decades of experience, I've built, maintained, and
          improved digital products with a particular emphasis on <strong>front-end development</strong>,
          team leadership, and delivering innovative products to market.
        </p>
        <p>
          Ensuring <strong>inclusivity</strong> is a top priority for me. I firmly believe that
          cultivating a diverse, safe, and respectful workplace and releasing products
          accessible to all is a collective responsibility. Outside work, I spend time with
          my fantastic family, explore <strong>photography</strong>, stay active through sport,
          play chess, build passion projects under <strong>pixari.dev</strong>,
          and coach fellow developers.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-photo reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <picture>
          <source
            srcset="/images/raffaele-pizzari-200.webp 200w, /images/raffaele-pizzari.webp 400w"
            sizes="(max-width: 600px) 150px, 200px"
            type="image/webp"
          />
          <img
            src="/images/raffaele-pizzari-200.jpg"
            srcset="/images/raffaele-pizzari-200.jpg 200w, /images/raffaele-pizzari-400.jpg 400w"
            sizes="(max-width: 600px) 150px, 200px"
            alt="Raffaele Pizzari"
            width="200"
            height="200"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
